## ğŸ†˜ Quick Troubleshooting Reference

**If app shows blank screen:**

- Check browser console (F12) for errors
- Verify Netlify build succeeded
- Check Firebase config is correct

**If login doesnâ€™t work:**

- Verify Firebase Authentication is enabled
- Check authorized domains in Firebase
- Verify no typos in email/password

**If grocery list wonâ€™t generate:**

- Verify GEMINI_API_KEY is set in Netlify
- Check you redeployed after adding key
- Verify Netlify Function logs for errors

**If data doesnâ€™t sync:**

- Verify both phones use same login
- Check internet connection
- Verify Firestore security rules are published

**For any issue:**

- Check browser console for errors
- Check Netlify deploy logs
- Check Netlify Function logs
- Ask Gemini with specific error messages

